  Scenario: Create user groups on the fly
    Given I am logged in as "admin"
    And the user group "Alte Gruppe"
    And I put "Mona Lisa" into the clipboard
    When I go to the clipboard
    And I follow "all"
    And I follow "Add to a global group"
